2587&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFI2%2Fv5hJrJLSiIP9i8i%2FMgDc%3D&h=6d5bba4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20150112%2Fs00001%2F1421070134664%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E7%259F%25B3%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E8%25AC%259B%25E8%25BE%25AD%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%2596%2587&h=d2d7907c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20150112/s00001/1421070134664/%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E5%85%AC%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E7%9F%B3%E6%B0%B8%E6%B3%B0%E8%AC%9B%E8%BE%AD%E5%85%A8%E6%96%87</a><br />\n<br />\n好文要再推<br />\n<br />\n衝爆塊玻璃只係犯法<br />\n政府以法律為己用打壓民眾先係衝擊法治<br />\n<br />\n唔好比政府大倒<br />\n<br />\n我冇野講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:12:00.000Z","msg":"呢兩句好到肉。<br />\n<br />\n//極權國家利用法律作為整治民眾的工具，而不是用法律約束自己管治的方式//<br />\n<br />\n//政府對人民擁有公權力，而權力容易令人腐化和被濫用，所以在有關法治的討論很自然會強調對政府公權力的約束//"}]}